{"tid":701288,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"愛因斯坦評中國人：勤勞、骯髒、遲鈍","createTime":"2018-06-14T04:32:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T05:59:28.000Z","uid":20933,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0d8d032784f88715ca3bc423300f4c1fa280c9fd","tid":701288,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:32:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180614/large/1528937692_b8d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180614%2Flarge%2F1528937692_b8d0.jpg&h=b75dccec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n著名物理學家愛因斯坦（Albert Einstein）的旅行日記曝光，他在記述1922年的亞洲之旅、在中國旅遊時，中國人是「勤勞、骯髒、遲鈍」，「吃飯時不坐在凳子上」。<br />\n<br />\n愛因斯坦的旅遊日記，是在一本由美國普林斯頓大學出版的新書《愛因斯坦旅遊日記，遠東、巴勒斯坦、西班牙，1922至1923》（The Travel Diaries of Albert Einstein: The Far East, Palestine, and Spain, 1922&ndash;1923），記錄他當年到新加坡、香港、中國、日本等亞洲地區的旅行日記。<br />\n<br />\n在日記中，愛因斯坦除形容中國人「勤勞、骯髒、遲鈍」，他形容中國人蹲着吃飯的樣子，「像歐洲人在叢林裏解手時一樣」，一切發生得悄無聲息且一本正經。他又稱中國人子嗣眾多、「繁殖力旺盛」，又稱「就連中國的孩子們看起來都無精打采、呆頭呆腦」，「（中國人）大多數負擔沉重&hellip;&hellip;他們似乎駑鈍得不理解自己命運的可怕」。<br />\n<br />\n愛因斯坦又指中國人「即使那些像馬一樣辛勞工作的人，也不會讓人覺得他們意識到痛苦。一個像羊群一樣的特殊民族，更像是機器而非人類」。<br />\n<br />\n相對於中國人，愛因斯坦形容日本人則相對積極：「日本人是低調的、體面的，總體來說非常吸引人的」，他更稱「（日本人有着）從其他地方的人們身上都難以看到的純潔靈魂。每個人都應該喜愛並羨慕這樣的國家」。<br />\n<br />\n美國加州理工大學愛因斯坦論文項目高級編輯羅克斯倫茨表示，愛因斯坦旅行日記中的很多言論「讓人不快」，尤其是他對中國人的內容，「這些言論和愛因斯坦的偉大人道主義偶像形像對比強烈」，羅克斯倫茨認為愛因斯坦在日記中所寫的，「比較放鬆警惕」，因為他「不打算出版這些日記」。"},{"pid":"e022c99d7c238780c5d3e5ee310967564a394bb5","tid":701288,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:32:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180614/58315829\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180614%2F58315829&d=q3Ak43684UhECaN9%2FTJep2Mi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=b0dc275b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180614%2F58315829&h=7ac98cc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180614/58315829</a>"},{"pid":"ad92c68022b1d81d56116b7fb76d80bb43af3e58","tid":701288,"uid":135957,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:38:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49e94a2a6807f9e14ed55a767f9e7401f8fcfc74","tid":701288,"uid":73310,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"ad92c68022b1d81d56116b7fb76d80bb43af3e58","tid":701288,"uid":135957,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:38:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:40:53.000Z","msg":"但句說話到今時今日都岩用,代表咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39ed2f77d225669d3c99504dbbb5b7fb619ea437","tid":701288,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:53:19.000Z","msg":"「蹲着」食飯啫，你估隨地「蹲着」大便咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b631bd7f7d521f6652992daffe03cd69c69b40","tid":701288,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:55:54.000Z","msg":"100年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d361d33af6f9ca9fa0aef6394021a29c835a623","tid":701288,"uid":52595,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:57:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b2de71af82291c21c1689fd21ce2329bd577b6a","tid":701288,"uid":177639,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:59:50.000Z","msg":"同香港一樣"},{"pid":"86b043fbb80b70b0fcb0ae9418eff72fd1245455","tid":701288,"uid":131691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T05:04:26.000Z","msg":"介紹本書俾大家：<br />\nRalph Townsend 嘅 Ways That Are Dark<br />\n1933年歧視中國民族嘅巨著<br />\n極度詳盡咁記載咗蝗蟲嘅行為舉止、待人處事嘅態度<br />\n係香港人嘅必讀反面教材<br />